While its website shows moderate local SEO performance, critical areas like Google Business Profile optimization are entirely unaddressed, leading to poor discoverability. This inconsistent online presence directly contributes to an unpredictable sales pipeline, hindering revenue growth. There is a clear and immediate opportunity to leverage targeted digital improvements to capture more local leads and stabilize business growth.
